        { "Description", "Emotes temporarily grant third-person camera access. Don\'t worry, though, we already made sure that this won\'t affect gameplay. Enemies behind walls can not be seen, heard, or smelled while emoting. No need to worry about enemies using emotes to gain an unfair advantage!" },
