        { "Title", "\240\159\147\156 A NOTE FROM THE DEVELOPERS" },
        { "Description", "Hey everyone, it\'s been a while since the last developer notes!" },
        { "Description", "We hope you all enjoyed the new gamemodes and the recent updates. We enjoyed working on them and providing a unique twist to how RIVALS can be played." },
